severe and chronic deterioration of personality and social functioning, often with minimal response to treatment.", "精神分裂症青春型:A subtype of schizophrenia characterized by emotional incongruity, bizarre behaviors, and symptoms like delusions and inappropriate actions, often diagnosed in younger patients."], "parameters": {"model": "text-embedding-v3"}}}